<plot>A Killer, lost on lonely country roads after disposing of the body, has a near-accident. Shaken, he finds his way into a strange ghost town, where he hopes to find directions. But the handful of people he encounters in a Barber's Shop are very odd, and seem to know more than they are willing to say. Befuddled, be exits, and finds he can't leave the town, when suddenly he has an encounter of the most bizarre kind, and learns a horrifying truth.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222051</url></doc>
